CO2 intensity of electricity.source: Calculated using 'Electricity Sales: Total Sales (BkWh)' and 'Emissions from the Electric Power Sector: Carbon Dioxide (MMst)' for each EMM region from the 2022 EIA Annual Energy Outlook (2021-2050), Table 54; previous years copied from previous versions of file based on previous AEOs
